The Countess of Wessex looked beautiful in a pink gingham dress and a matching hat. Sophie Wessex chose a very elegant pink and cream gingham suit for the special occasion. The royal combined the look with a  matching hat. For jewellery, she was seen wearing a pearl necklace, a silver bracelet and a pair of silver earrings. Sophie was all smiles in the carriage with her husband and children and waving at the crowds. READ MORE: Kate will star on Buckingham Palace balcony without Meghan - pictures The Countess of Wessex styled her hair in a chic low bun. Her Majesty and other members of the Royal Family including the Duke and Duchess of Cambridge, Prince Charles and the Duchess of Cornwall and Princess Anne were also present. More to follow...'